          <p class="ps18"><span class="ts15">&nbsp;2. NASAAN ANG BANSANG PINILI</span></p>
        </td>
        <td class="cell0">
          <p class="ps19"><a href="idh-topic40.htm" title=" 1. ANG BANAL NA CIUDAD NG JERUSALEM"><img width="32" height="32" border="0" src="images/navigation%20links/previous%20bluetriangles32.png" /></a><a href="idh-topic30.htm" title="Topics Outline"><img width="32" height="32" border="0" src="images/navigation%20links/parent%20silverarrows32.png" /></a><a href="idh-topic80.htm" title=" 3. ANG TUNAY NA KAHULUGAN NA ANG BAGONG JERUSALEM AY NAGMULA SA LANGIT"><img width="32" height="32" border="0" src="images/navigation%20links/next%20bluetriangles32.png" /></a></p>
